[normal]People in Northern Ireland have told us they use branches of banks quite regularly. Eight in ten (80%) visited a branch of a bank at least once in the past year, six in ten (60%) in the last month and three in ten (32%) in the last week.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
