[normal]Areas the committee could consider further[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Structure and [bold]Regulation[bold] of banks[bold]:[bold]How can consumers be assured
[normal] that the FCA are taking necessary steps following the payments crisis in 2012 following their decision to not publis
[normal]h a report or any information on
[normal] their work to date.
